></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n繼打，呢隻好用？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絲*</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搽之前要用小小濕嘅紙巾抹走啲爛爛哋嘅嘴皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時有層膜喺度嘅話，可以搽一層潤唇膏，等一陣之後再抹走佢就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再搽潤唇膏就超ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可能你會覺得好煩，但好多潤唇膏都係要咁，又唔係100% natural<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb6e10c570a40318c5ec3338b9df26f9a8af763b","tid":32730,"uid":13700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T19:18:54.000Z","msg":"Thanks 絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}